2.  **Goal**: We need to show `iIndepFun (fun p ω => ω p.2 p.1) (Bandit.streamMeasure ν)`. This means for any natural number `n`, the function `g_n := (fun p ω => ω p.2 p.1) ∘ (fun ω ↦ ω n)` is independent with respect to `Bandit.streamMeasure ν`.

